Firewood is a 2D adventure game with psychological horror elements

The game tells the story of an old man who has lost his wife years
ago and is still having troubles with his past

After his wife's funeral, he decides to move to a cabin far away
from town in order to escape from the haunting memories of the past
and his country's opressive regime

Yet one day, events take an unexpected turn and he finds himself in
a dark journey

Will he be able to find the redemption he seeks?

Side scrolling 2D adventure game with hand drawn graphics
Grim and atmospheric music
A twisting story
